11.1 Discrete-Time Approximation
	•	Integrators for F, p, A, \Pi.

11.2 Parameterization of Metrics
	•	Choice of M and N.
	•	Constraints for stability.

11.3 Numerical Examples
	•	Small relational systems (n=2, n=3).

